attributes.value: Values loyalty
Respects power
Sees sacrifice as wasteful and foolish
Sees perseverance in the face of adversity as bull-headed and foolish
Sees war as a useful means to an end
Never falls in love or develops positive feelings toward anything
Desires little for herself in the way of possessions
Feels strong urges and seeks short-term rewards
Is generally quite confident of her abilities when undertaking specific ventures
Could not care less about her appearance, talents or other personal vanities
Has no ambition whatsoever
Does not generally seek retribution for past wrongs
Generally finds herself quite hopeful about the future
Hates vows, obligations, promises and other binding elements that could restrict her
Can sometimes act without deliberation
Tries to keep her things orderly
Prefers to be alone
Dislikes abstract discussions and would much rather focus on practical examples
Strong
Slow to tire
Quick to heal
A very good sense of the position of her own body
